\par
\pard\nowidctlpar\fi-360\li360\tx360 1.\tab Maximize Bomb Shelter.\line\par
2.\tab In the \b Bomb Shelter\b0  dialog box, click \b Properties\b0 .\line\par
3.\tab In the \b Error Protection\b0  group, click \b Advanced\b0 .\line\par
4.\tab In the \b Advanced Properties\b0  tab, deselect the \b Write Protect VMM\b0  check box.\line\par
5.\tab Click \b Apply\b0  or \b OK\b0 , and then click \b OK\b0  on all subsequent screens.\par
