\pard{\pntext\f6\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf6\pnindent360{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sb100\sa100 Teams are now persisted for the next game when map cycling occurs \par
{\pntext\f6\'B7\tab}Map Reset: It's now possible to restart the current game without requiring the server to map cycle. \par
