{\pntext\f6\'B7\tab}Assault: Alongside this timer, we also have an "Offense" and "Deffense" indicator to quickly inform you of your role \par
\pard\sb100\sa100\line\b Addressing the Most Frequent Issues Experienced by Gamers\b0\par
Many users have reported problems with Halo PC when using 3rd party software to force the refresh rate of their monitor. We have changed how we handle this situation in our code to seamlessly fall back to the forced refresh rate. \par
A significant number of reported game crashes are related to an external library called keystone.dll. We have updated this library to address the most common failures. These crashes would usually occur when changing screen resolution, when starting or quitting Halo PC, when chatting in a multiplayer game or when using ALT-TAB to minimize Halo PC and return to Windows. \par
